00:11:49.480 --> 00:11:59.880
is just matrix multiplication. So this is very&nbsp;
much an A3 Prime type of definition. We are just&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:11:59.880 --> 00:12:08.720
giving a description of a set, a set in quotes,&nbsp;
very big quotes, and a description of matrix&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:17.160
multiplication as being the multiplication that's&nbsp;
